title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - December 14, 2021
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - December 14, 2021
description:
Gary and Mark link up and review some of the text messages coming out of the January 6th commission and also discuss a seeming miscarriage of justice coming out of a New York courtroom. 

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
